text: WMVX may refer to: * WMVX (AM), a radio station (1110 AM) located in Salem, New Hampshire, United States * WUBG (AM), a radio station (1570 AM) located in Methuen, Massachusetts, United States, which held the WMVX call sign from 2012 to 2017 * WHLK, a radio station (106.5 FM) located in Cleveland, Ohio, United States, which held the WMVX call sign from 1997 to 2011
title: WMVX
